quran[52]{c,v,t}:
  69,1,Choonadi chenicheni
  69,2,Kodi choonadi chenicheni ndi chiyani
  69,3,Kodi ndi chiyani chimene chingakupangitse kuti udziwe kuti choonadi chenicheni ndi chiti
  69,4,Mtundu wa Thamoud ndi Ad adakana ola la chionongeko
  69,5,Ndipo anthu a Thamoud adaonongeka ndi mfuwu woopsya
  69,6,Ndipo anthu a Aad adaonongeka ndi chimphepo cha mkuntho
  69,7,Chimene Mulungu adachilamulira kuti chikunthe pa iwo usiku usanu ndi uwiri ndi usana usanu ndi utatu mosalekeza. Moti iwe ukadawaona anthu atagonagona ukadayesa kuti ndi mitengo ya migwalangwa yakugwa
  69,8,Kodi uli kuona wina wa iwo opulumuka
  69,9,"Ndipo Farao ndi anthu amene adalipo iye asadabadwe, ndi a mizinda imene idaonongeka anali kuchita zoipa"
  69,10,Ndipo iwo sanamvere Mtumwi wochokera kwa Ambuye wawo ndipo Iye adawalanga ndi chilango chowawa zedi
  69,11,"Ndithudi!Pamenemadzianasefukira,Ifetidakunyamulani inu m’chombo"
  69,12,Kuti tikhoza kuchipanga icho kukhala chikumbutso ndi kuti khutu la kumva limve
  69,13,Ndipo pamene lipenga lidzaimbidwa kamodzi
  69,14,Ndipo nthaka ndi mapiri anyamulidwa pamodzi ndi kuponyedwa pansi mwamphamvu kamodzi
  69,15,Patsiku limeneli chinthu choopsa chidzachitika
  69,16,Ndipo thambo lidzaphwanyika ndipo lidzakhala lopanda mphamvu
  69,17,Ndipo Angelo adzaima mbali zonse ndipo angelo asanu ndi atatu pa tsikuli adzanyamula Mpando wa Chifumu wa Ambuye wako
  69,18,Patsiku limeneli mudzaweruzidwa ndipo palibe chinthu chachinsinsi chimene chidzabisika
  69,19,"Ndipo yense amene adzapatsidwa Buku lake kudzanja lamanja adzati: “Ah taonani! Werengani Buku langa!”"
  69,20,"Ndithudi, ine ndidakhululupira kuti tsiku lina zochita zanga zidzaweruzidwa"
  69,21,Kotero iye adzakhala ndi moyo wa chisangalalo
  69,22,M’munda wapamwamba
  69,23,Wa zipatso zokoma zimene zili pafupi
  69,24,Idyani ndipo imwani mmene mufunire chifukwa cha ntchito zanu zabwino zimene mudatumiza patsogolo panu m’masiku apitawo
  69,25,"Koma iye amene adzapatsidwe buku lake m’dzanja lamanzere, adzati: “Kukadakhala bwino ngati Buku langa likadakhala losaperekedwa kwa ine.”"
  69,26,“Ndipo sindikadziwa kuti zochita zanga zachuluka bwanji.”
  69,27,“Ikadakhala bwino imfa ikadangodza pa ine.”
  69,28,“Chuma changa sichidandithandize chilichonse.”
  69,29,“Ulamuliro wanga wonse wachoka kwa ine.”
  69,30,“Mugwireni ndipo mumumange.”
  69,31,“Ndipo m’ponyeni M’ng’anjo ya moto.”
  69,32,“Ndipo mumangeni ndi unyolo wotalika malipande makumi asanu ndi awiri.”
  69,33,"Ndithudi, iye samakhulupirira mwa Mulungu wamkulu"
  69,34,Ndipo sadali kuthandiza kudyetsa anthu osowa
  69,35,Motero lero iye sadzakhala ndi bwenzi aliyense
  69,36,Kapena chakudya china chilichonse kupatula zonyasa zochoka pa zilonda
  69,37,Palibe amene adzachidya kupatula ochimwa ndi osakhulupilira
  69,38,Motero Ine ndilumbira pali chilichonse chimene uli nkuona
  69,39,Ndi chimene chili chobisika
  69,40,Kuti ndithudi awa ndi mawu a Mtumwi wolemekezeka
  69,41,Ndipo si mawu a Mlakatuli ayi ndipo chikhulupiriro chanu ndi chochepa
  69,42,"Ndipo si mawu a munthu wa maula ayi, ndipo ndi zochepa zimene inu mukumbukira"
  69,43,Ichi ndi chivumbulutso chochokera kwa Ambuye wa zolengedwa zonse
  69,44,Ndipo iye akanapeka nkhani yokhudza Ife
  69,45,Ndithudi Ife tikadagwira dzanja lake lamanja
  69,46,"Ndipo, ndithudi, Ifetikadadulamtsemphawakewamoyo"
  69,47,"Ndipo palibe, wina wa inu, amene akadatiletsa Ife kumugwira"
  69,48,"Ndipo, ndithudi, Korani iyi ndi chikumbutso kwa iwo amene amapewa zoipa"
  69,49,"Ndipo, ndithudi, Ife timadziwa kuti alipo ena a inu amene amaikana"
  69,50,"Ndipo, ndithudi, ilo lidzakhala lomvetsa chisoni kwa anthu osakhulupirira"
  69,51,"Ndipo, ndithudi, ichi ndi choonadi chokhachokha"
  69,52,"Motero lemekeza dzina la Ambuye wako, Wamkulu kulu"